a","name":"shreepadma","key":"shreepadma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Shreepadma Venugopalan","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2013-06-05T21:24:41.263+0000","updated":"2013-06-05T21:24:41.263+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12650379/comment/13676402","id":"13676402","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"If the main use case is row-level security, then I think we're better off adding this functionality in a way that makes the additional work visible to the optimizer, e.g. with views.\n\nI think it would help to provide some more details about the motivation for this patch, possibly including a concrete use-case as well. Thanks.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2013-06-05T21:57:42.581+0000","updated":"2013-06-05T21:57:42.581+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12650379/comment/13676521","id":"13676521","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=shreepadma","name":"shreepadma","key":"shreepadma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Shreepadma Venugopalan","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"This is a general purpose hook and is not specific to any feature. Hive has hooks at various stages of compilation and execution - pre semantic analysis, post semantic analysis, pre execution etc, but misses a post execution/post fetch hook. This JIRA just adds that.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=shreepadma","name":"shreepadma","key":"shreepadma","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Shreepadma Venugopalan","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2013-06-06T00:02:54.360+0000","updated":"2013-06-06T00:02:54.360+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12650379/comment/13676588","id":"13676588","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Ok, but can you give me an actual example of something that requires this functionality?\n\nWhat kind of information do you plan to make available to the hook?\n\nI also think we need to be really careful about providing a way for people to mutate the resultset after it has been generated since this work will be done on the server node in a non-distributed fashion.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2013-06-06T01:36:29.849+0000","updated":"2013-06-06T01:36:29.849+0000"}],"maxResults":5,"total":5,"startAt":0},"votes":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/HIVE-4641/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_12311820":"0|i1l1y7:"}}